---
title: Seared Lamb Steak with Potato Mash & Mint Sauce
description: Known as the salmon of the land, these lean lamb steaks and vitamin-packed sides become the perfect guilt-free dinner without skimping on the flavour. Top it off with a drizzle of buttery mint sauce for a herby hit of heaven.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-lamb-steak-3aef67c4.jpg
